OL,3,CHuw Edwards pleads guilty to making
OL,4,Cindecent images of children
OL,6,FFormer BBC presenter Huw Edwards has
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to three counts of
OL,8,Fmaking indecent images of children.
OL,10,FThe 62-year-old was flanked by police
OL,11,Fofficers and swarmed by photographers
OL,12,Fas he made his way to Westminster
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,15,FPhotographers were knocked around as
OL,16,Fthey scrambled to get to Edwards, one
OL,17,Fof them had their camera smashed.
OL,19,FEdwards refused to answer any
OL,20,Fquestions.
