OL,3,CHuw Edwards pleads guilty to making
OL,4,Cindecent images of children
OL,6,FThe veteran broadcaster is accused of
OL,7,Fhaving had 37 photographs on WhatsApp,
OL,8,Fincluding six of the most serious type
OL,9,F- between December 2020 and April 2022.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Metropolitan
OL,12,FPolice said he was arrested in
OL,13,FNovember last year and charged on June
OL,14,F26.
