OL,3,CHuw Edwards pleads guilty to making
OL,4,Cindecent images of children
OL,6,FAccording to the charge sheet, Edwards
OL,7,Fis accused of having six category A
OL,8,Fimages, 12 category B pictures and 19
OL,9,Fcategory C photographs on WhatsApp `
OL,10,Foffences contrary to sections 1(1)(a)
OL,11,Fand 6 of the Protection of Children
OL,12,FAct 1978.
OL,14,FHe could receive a maximum penalty of
OL,15,Ften years' imprisonment.
OL,17,FEdwards was one of the BBC's most
OL,18,Fprominent and highest-paid news
OL,19,Fanchors before he left the corporation
OL,20,Fin April on medical grounds.
