OL,6,FDuring his career, he fronted BBC's
OL,7,FNews At Ten for 20 years and anchored
OL,8,Fcoverage of major national events
OL,9,Fincluding announcing Queen Elizabeth
OL,10,FII's death on the BBC and presenting
OL,11,Fcoverage of her funeral.
OL,13,FHe was previously the BBC's highest-
OL,14,Fpaid newsreader, with a pay bracket of
OL,15,F#475,000 to #479,999 for the year 2023/
OL,16,F24 for 160 presenting days, BBC One
OL,17,Fnews specials, election specials and
OL,18,Fother television programming,
OL,19,Faccording to the corporation's latest
OL,20,Fannual report.
